OL,3,CDriver dies in St Brelade car collision
OL,5,FA 78-year-old driver has died
OL,6,Ffollowing a road traffic collision in
OL,7,FSt Brelade on Sunday, the States of
OL,8,FJersey Police have confirmed.
OL,10,FPolice were called to a collision
OL,11,Fbetween two vehicles on Route des
OL,12,FGenets at approximately 14:50. One
OL,13,Fperson was taken to hospital and later
OL,14,Fdied.
OL,16,FPolice say that an investigation into
OL,17,Fthe incident is ongoing.
